  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the best form of dietary intervention to
      undernourished individuals with COPD.

      The research aims to test the null hypothesis that there is no difference between oral
      nutritional supplements and dietary advice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
